  EffectDiscription_ENG: This card/Digimon is also treated as having [Sakuyamon]
    in its name. [When Digivolving] You may use an Option card with a cost of 5 or
    less in your hand without paying the cost. [Your Turn][Once Per Turn] When you
    use an Option card with a cost of 2 or more, you may play 1 [Taomon] or 1 level
    4 or lower yellow or blue Digimon card from this Digimon's digivolution cards
    without paying the cost.
